Revision history for Mxpress-PDF

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

0.21    2020-04-13
	- Fix a warning when justifying text.

0.23    2020-04-13
	- Add new plugin Mxpres::PDF::Plugin::Border

0.24    2020-04-13
	- Fix for nested TOC outlines.

0.25    2020-04-25
	- New attribute concat in Mxpress::PDF::Plugin::Text that aids in concatenating text segments.
	- Add an example to synopsis of switching between default, bold, italic fonts.

0.26    2020-04-25
	- Extend Mxpress::PDF::Plugin::Line to allow for line styles (dots, dashed and custom)

0.27    2020-04-27
	- Add new plugin Mxpress::PDF::Plugin::List that aids in rendering bullet point lists.
